6.title: Exclusive Interview with Rosey Grier
6.plot: Exclusive Interview with Roosevelt "Rosey" Grier, an American actor, singer, Christian minister, and former professional American football player. He was a notable college football player for The Pennsylvania State University who earned a retrospective place in the National Collegiate Athletic Association 100th anniversary list of 100 most influential student athletes. As a professional player, Grier was a member of the New York Giants and the original Fearsome Foursome of the Los Angeles Rams. He played in the Pro Bowl twice.

imdb.plot outline: Actors Reporter hosts, themselves entertainment professionals, interview working actors, singers, comics, producers, directors and others in the entertainment industry. Guests share stories about their childhood, how they began in the business, their journey and helpful suggestions for others who aspire to their profession.
imdb.title: Actors Reporter Interviews
plot: Exclusive up-close and personal interviews with working actors and the entertainment industry.::Pepper Jay

Actors Reporter hosts, themselves entertainment professionals, interview working actors, singers, comics, producers, directors and others in the entertainment industry. Guests share stories about their childhood, how they began in the business, their journey and helpful suggestions for others who aspire to their profession.::Pepper Jay
